sql:
SELECT AVG(income) AS average_income
FROM demographic_data
WHERE industry = 'Healthcare' AND job_title = 'Prof-specialty';

external_knowledge:
- Self-emp refers to individuals who are self-employed; 
- Private refers to individuals working in the private sector; 
- Average age is the average of the ages of the individuals in the specified category; 
- Average capital gain is the average of the capital gains earned by the individuals in the specified category; 
- Average capital loss is the average of the capital losses incurred by the individuals in the specified category; 
- Average hours worked per week is the average of the hours worked per week by the individuals in the specified category.

